{"id":232857650,"title":"#分享 台灣圖標字型小遊戲","content":"大家安安\n\n昨天看到一個蠻酷的 icon set\nhttps://www.twicon.page/index.html\n\n基本上就是以台灣做為出發點的一套圖標字型\n仔細一看就會發現這個網頁用到的所有圖示\n主題都是圍繞著台灣的特有元素\nlike 國旗，夜市，大同電鍋\n當然還有被日本人玩壞的珍珠奶茶 (誤\n\n有趣的是兩位設計師都不是台灣人\n但看到這個專案當下真的蠻感動的\n\n如果人在海外的話\n我想感受應該更為深刻\n\n都有這麼好的素材不好好善用就可惜了\n所以我做了一個簡單的網頁小遊戲\nMobile 有簡單做調整\n所以也可以直接在手機上玩\n\nDEMO 連結底加\nhttps://weichiachang.github.io/twicon-game\n\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/8k7njxu.jpg\n\n\n原始碼寫得有點亂，但歡迎發 Issue 或直接來個 PR\nhttps://github.com/WeiChiaChang/twicon-game\n\nBtw，希望大家玩完之後\n這週六都能撥空返鄉投個票\n\n謝謝","excerpt":"大家安安，昨天看到一個蠻酷的 icon set，基本上就是以台灣做為出發點的一套圖標字型，仔細一看就會發現這個網頁用到的所有圖示，主題都是圍繞著台灣的特有元素，like 國旗，夜市，大同電鍋，當然還有","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"a6dc1b6b-0aca-4004-86c8-3af6cdbfad23","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-09T11:06:03.116Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-09T11:08:36.904Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":17,"tags":[],"topics":["前端工程","遊戲","台灣","字型","台灣人"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"軟體工程師","forumAlias":"softwareengineer","school":"國立臺灣科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":17}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/8k7njxu.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"d2d4657c-7878-46dd-ad9c-030758157527","url":"https://i.imgur.com/8k7njxul.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/8k7njxul.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/8k7njxul.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-09T11:08:36.904Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-09T11:08:36.904Z"},{"id":"d2d4657c-7878-46dd-ad9c-030758157527","url":"http://i.imgur.com/8k7njxu.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/8k7njxu","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/8k7njxul.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"c